            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Sex</abbr><ex>to</ex></expan> Allio Mamerco <lb n="2"/>pontifici perpetuo <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>col</abbr><ex>oniae</ex></expan> Astigitanae <lb n="4"/>et <lb n="5"/>flamini <expan><abbr>divor</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>August</abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>concili IMMVNES <lb n="7"/>ILIENSES ILSIPENSES <lb n="8"/>VIRITIM statuam <lb n="9"/><abbr>d</abbr> <abbr>d</abbr>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Das Stück ist heute verschollen. Lesung nach Carbonell (16. Jh.). Überlieferung bei Roa (1629): SEX. AELIO M[---] / C N TITI CILER[---] / C[---]C[---]A[---]E[---] / FL[---]M[---]D [---] OR AVGVS.[---] / CONCI[---] C [---]A [---]NIS / CONS [---]F NEE / [---] STATVAM / ------.</p>
            </div>
